# 💰 Expense Tracker - Spring Boot Application

A backend application built using **Spring Boot** and **MySQL** to manage daily expenses.  
Users can add, update, delete, and view their expenses with summary reports.

---

## 🚀 Features

- Add a new expense with description and amount
- Update existing expenses
- Delete an expense
- View all expenses
- View monthly expense summary
- User authentication & authorization (if added)

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Java 17**
- **Spring Boot 3.x**
- **Spring Data JPA**
- **MySQL**
- **Maven**
- **Spring Security & JWT** (if implemented)

---
